(10092, 'System - JU Tooltip', 'plugin', 'jutooltip', 'system', 0, 1, 1, 0, '{\"name\":\"System - JU Tooltip\",\"type\":\"plugin\",\"creationDate\":\"Sep 2012\",\"author\":\"JoomUltra\",\"copyright\":\"Copyright (C) 2010 - 2012 JoomUltra. All rights reserved.\",\"authorEmail\":\"admin@joomultra.com\",\"authorUrl\":\"www.joomlultra.com\",\"version\":\"2.5.0\",\"description\":\"\\n\\t\\t\\n\\t\\t<div style=\'font-weight: normal\'>\\n\\t\\t<h2 style=\'color: #0A71A5;\'>JU Tooltip Plugin<\\/strong><\\/h2>\\n\\t\\t<span style=\'color: #ff0000;\'><strong>Features:<\\/strong><\\/span>\\n\\t\\t<br\\/>\\n\\t\\tLoad tooltip for any element.\\n\\t\\t<br\\/><br\\/>\\n\\t\\t<strong><span style=\'color: #ff0000;\'>Usage Instructions:<\\/span><\\/strong><br \\/>\\n\\t\\tRequirements: Joomla! 2.5.x, Joomla! 3.0.x<br\\/>\\n\\t\\tThis module require jQuery javascript library to work. If jQuery has not been loaded on your site, you should install <b>Plugin JU Load jQuery<\\/b>.<br\\/><br\\/>\\n\\t\\tAdd <strong>class=\\\"jutooltip\\\" title=\\\"your tooltip content\\\"<\\/strong> for the html tag you want to display tooltip.\\n\\t\\t<br \\/><br \\/>\\n\\t\\t<strong>Example:<\\/strong><br\\/>\\n\\t\\t<ol>\\n\\t\\t  <li>1. Load tooltip from title attribute. HTML: <i>&lt;a class=\\\"jutooltip\\\" title=\\\"This is my tooltip\\\"&gt;Hover me&lt;\\/a&gt;<\\/i><\\/li>\\n\\t\\t  <li>2. Load manual html tooltip, by don\'t set title attribute then use content of next tag as tooltip. By this way, you can use any html for tooltip. HTML: <i>&lt;a class=\\\"jutooltip\\\">Hover me&lt;\\/a&gt; &lt;div style=\\\"display: none;\\\"&gt;Manual &lt;b&gt;html tag&lt;\\/b&gt; next the &lt;strong>tooltip&lt;\\/strong&gt; will be display as tooltip&lt;\\/div&gt;<\\/i><\\/li>\\n\\t\\t  <li>3. Use single tooltip for multi trigger elements, by this way, you can re-format html for tooltip use defined id\\/class CSS. For example, if you set <strong>Single tooltip: .myredtip<\\/strong>. HTML: <i>&lt;a class=\\\"jutooltip\\\" title=\\\"This is my tooltip\\\"&gt;Hover me&lt;\\/a&gt;&lt;div class=\\\"myredtip\\\"&gt;Title attribute will be loaded here, you can use class myredtip to re-format this tag&lt;\\/div&gt;<\\/i><\\/li>\\n\\t\\t<\\/ol>\\n\\t\\t<br \\/><br \\/>\\n\\t\\t<strong><span style=\'color: #ff0000;\'>Upgrade Methods:<\\/span><br \\/><\\/strong>\\n\\t\\t<ol>\\n\\t\\t  <li>Standard joomla uninstall \\/ reinstall method. Module supports upgrade method. <\\/li>\\n\\t\\t  <li>You can install new version directly over this version. Uninstallation is not required. <\\/li>\\n\\t\\t  <li>Backup any customized file before upgrading.<\\/li>\\n\\t\\t<\\/ol>\\n\\t\\t<br \\/><br \\/>\\n\\t\\tIf you use JU Tooltip, please post a review for <a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/extensions.joomla.org\\/extensions\\/news-display\\/article-elements\\/tooltips\\/22717\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\" title=\\\"Post a review for JU Tooltip\\\">JU Tooltip on JED<\\/a>\\n\\t\\t<p>Copyright 2010 - 2013 <a href=\'http:\\/\\/www.joomultra.com\\/\' title=\'Visit JoomUltra.com!\'>JoomUltra.com<\\/a>.<\\/p>\\n\\t\\t<\\/div>\\n\\t\\t\\n\\t\",\"group\":\"\",\"filename\":\"jutooltip\"}', '{\"loadjquery\":\"2\",\"loadjqueryfrom\":\"1\",\"theme\":\"default\",\"showtooltipwhen\":\"mouseenter\",\"effect\":\"slide\",\"slide_direction\":\"left\",\"slide_bounce\":\"false\",\"slideOffset\":10,\"showDuration\":200,\"hideDuration\":200,\"easing\":\"linear\",\"predelay\":0,\"delay\":30,\"opacity\":\"1\",\"tip\":\"\",\"fadeIE\":\"false\",\"horizontal\":\"left\",\"vertical\":\"center\",\"offset\":\"[0, 0]\",\"cancelDefault\":\"true\",\"manualCloseTooltip\":\"false\"}', '', '', 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 7, 0),
(10093, 'Vina Article Carousel', 'module', 'mod_vina_carousel_content', '', 0, 1, 0, 0, '{\"name\":\"Vina Article Carousel\",\"type\":\"module\",\"creationDate\":\"July 15, 2014\",\"author\":\"VinaGecko.com\",\"copyright\":\"Copyright (C) 2014 VinaGecko.com. All rights reserved.\",\"authorEmail\":\"admin@vinagecko.com\",\"authorUrl\":\"http:\\/\\/VinaGecko.com\",\"version\":\"1.1\",\"description\":\"\\n\\t\\t<div style=\\\"border: 1px solid red; border-radius: 7px; padding: 10px;\\\">\\n\\t\\t\\tWe are pleased to announce that we have released new module for <strong>Joomla 3.x<\\/strong>: <strong>Vina Article Carousel<\\/strong>. This module will help you to show more articles of <strong>Content Component<\\/strong> in beautiful <strong>responsive carousel slider<\\/strong>. It has options for setting the pagination\\/sliding speed, enabling\\/disabling autoplay, showing bullet navigation and more. Module is very flexible, easy to install and configure!<br\\/><br\\/>\\n\\t\\t\\t<strong>VinaGecko.com<\\/strong> - Premium <a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/vinagecko.com\\/joomla-modules\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">Joomla Modules<\\/a>, <a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/vinagecko.com\\/joomla-plugins\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">Joomla Plugins<\\/a>, <a href=\\\"http:\\/\\/vinagecko.com\\/joomla-templates\\\" target=\\\"_blank\\\">Joomla Templates<\\/a>.\\n\\t\\t<\\/div>\\n\\t\",\"group\":\"\",\"filename\":\"mod_vina_carousel_content\"}', '{\"moduleWidth\":\"100%\",\"moduleHeight\":\"auto\",\"moduleMargin\":\"0px\",\"modulePadding\":\"10px 5px\",\"bgImage\":\"\",\"isBgColor\":\"1\",\"bgColor\":\"#CCCCCC\",\"itemMargin\":\"0 5px\",\"itemPadding\":\"10px\",\"isItemBgColor\":\"1\",\"itemBgColor\":\"#FFFFFF\",\"itemTextColor\":\"#333333\",\"itemLinkColor\":\"#0088CC\",\"items\":\"4\",\"itemsDesktop\":\"[1170,4]\",\"itemsDesktopSmall\":\"[980,3]\",\"itemsTablet\":\"[800,3]\",\"itemsTabletSmall\":\"[650,2]\",\"itemsMobile\":\"[450,1]\",\"singleItem\":\"0\",\"itemsScaleUp\":\"0\",\"slideSpeed\":\"200\",